![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252083951-2D9IFUMCPUMEJLST27GW/image-asset.jpeg)

Anung Un Rama. Big Red. Hellboy. With his reboot right around the corner, it seemed poetic to study what makes the demonic do-godder tick. From his explosive debut, to being featured on the big screen, Hellboy is the protagonist we never knew we wanted. We talk BPRD, Lobster Johnson, Guillermo del Toro, and rosted peanuts as the Don digs deep with Hellboy SUPER-fan Dalin Rowell and the incredible Peter Melnick of [The Marvelists!](https://www.facebook.com/themarvelists/)

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
